Description: Nosey
        -----
        
        Local continuous test runner with nose and watchdog.
        
        
        Nosey is easy to set up
        ```````````````````````
        
        ::
        
            $ pip install nosey
            $ cd myproject
            $ nosey
             * Watching /path/to/myproject
        
        
        Links
        `````
        
        * `Website <http://github.com/joeyespo/nosey>`_
        
        
